  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since then-- since then, they wouldn't let us back in the school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They would let us go to Hungarian schools, not to Czech schools.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because the Czechs themselves couldn't go to school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's not only Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They closed the schools.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So Jewish used to go-- would go to Hungarian schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I didn't--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't speak-- I didn't know how to speak Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was hanging, hanging out with other kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, I, I-- idle all the time, sometimes helping my, my father in store on a Thursday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But most of the time, I didn't have much work to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I would read books.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I would go out to see a movie with other guys.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Playing soccer was my favorite game.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in winter time, I would-- ice skating.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would-- in summer, I would go swimming, also, with, with other kids.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I behaved like a normal-- like other kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But my father didn't like it because I started to play cards, too-- with other kids playing cards.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother would give me-- my father wouldn't give me money.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He would-- he would-- and my mother would give me sometimes money to go and play cards with all the boys.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when he-- when he-- once, he caught me playing cards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He give me the-- he beat the hell out of me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I wouldn't-- I didn't like it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, oh, if I cannot stay home and do my, my things which I like to do, then I-- I'm going to have to look somewhere else to go and learn some kind of a skill, some trade.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I heard that my-- it was in 1938-- my-- like, in autumn, the end of summer, I heard that a cousin of mine, he went to Brunn.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Brunn is the capital of Moravia.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A province of Czechoslovakia called Moravia-- and the capital of that province is called Brunn, or Brno in Czech.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Over there-- his mother told me that [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Fred ?] is in Brunn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to my mother, I'm going to Brunn-- to [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fred. ?] Maybe I'll do what he's doing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one day, I went with my friends to see a movie.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I didn't tell my mother that I'm going.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I told her I would like to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But I didn't tell her when and, and, and how.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I just-- I said-- talked to my friends.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm going to, to Brunn to see [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Fred. ?] And my friends, [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Bela ?] and [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Fred, ?] they were my best friends.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were like buddies all the-- all the time, pals.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We went to the same class-- school buddies.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they come to say goodbye to me to the train station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I said, goodbye.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I'm going.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I just took a, a small bundle of things from the-- when we saw the movie was over, they showed us-- showed me off to the train.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I, I boarded the train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I bought a ticket-- Bustino to Brunn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It took me a whole day go get there, because the train didn't run properly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was all kind of-- had to stop over and wait for another train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So it took me almost-- more than a day to get to Brunn.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I came to Brunn.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I had never been in a big city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I didn't know where, where he is.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I don't know his address.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I was lost in this city.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, I went-- I found a Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw written, 'Jewish Community.' And I was asking-- yeah, I, I remembered the name of the place were [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fred's ?] supposed to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They called it 'Stiassni.' Stiassni was the biggest textile factory in Czechoslovakia, the biggest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So finally I got to the Stiassni office.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was asking for a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I said-- I, I had the school clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They don't accept no more us in school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I am from Bustino, from the-- Carpathia.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I would like to work something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I showed them some sketches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I brought with me also sketch-- what I am sketching.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I can do something which in textiles they use for, for sketching.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, OK, we will-- we will give you a job.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He give me a job.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I went to the-- to the cafeteria to have lunch, I, I met my friend [?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Freddie ?] over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was very happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he took me to his-- where he lives, where he rented a room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I rented a bed in, in, in the same room he was sleeping with this [?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Fred. ?] And we were very happy.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
